{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6fa36914e6","title":"杂文——带头","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"413882850b","index":0,"year":1956,"month":8,"day":31,"articleId":"6fa36914e6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"},{"id":"d54ce1c9cb","name":"苏金伞"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6f13d49b36","type":"title","text":"杂文——带头","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"409314c8fe","type":"authors","text":"河南苏金伞","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"4228e9bc34","type":"subtitle","text":"(苏金伞：诗人，河南省文联主席，河南省政协常委、人大代表)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"38972ac9ec","type":"paragraph","text":"先进带后进，本是推进工作，开展运动，带动社会前进的好方法。但就在这大家公认的规律上，却也常常发生问题。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"c582c7e6f4","type":"paragraph","text":"不久以前，安阳动员农民打井，打井本来是解决农村水利问题的一个最好的措施，但由于缺乏砖石，农民须挖窍门，想办法。某乡的支都书记就动员农民“挖”祖坟，并“带头”首先“挖”了自己的祖坟。农民在他这样“带头”之下，纷纷挖起祖坟来，有的挖开坟墓对着尸骨说：“老爷爷，请你也帮助我们建设社会主义吧！”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"083341d4ee","type":"paragraph","text":"乡支部书记为了动员大家打井，带头挖了自己的祖坟，其真心为社会主义，是很感动人的，可惜影响却很不好，实在出乎他的意料之外。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"c47c3ab913","type":"paragraph","text":"可见“头”也不能乱“带”，乱“带”，就会带出恶结果。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"a5dcbd98ce","type":"paragraph","text":"即使是最好的事情，带头也要首先带动思想，如果以自己的“带头”，“逼着”群众照自己的样子作，实际上那是变相的强迫命令，好事也会作成坏事的。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"212d32f3a5","type":"paragraph","text":" （人民日报1956年8月31日）","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"},{"id":"9b765ec860","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6"}],"page":{"id":"0818b5ccac","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6fa36914e6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}